Hey Raidernick! Just wanted to say: your mods are amazing! I love them! Of course mods like BDB, and Tantares exist, I still love to use your mods, even if the graphics might not be best quality, the detail, is amazing! As a suggestion: do you think you could try and add some sort of Zenit spy satellite? Even though it is probably one of the most launched and influenced the Vostok and Voskhod programs, it's very difficult to find a mod that creates the satellite. And if you wanted to expand on this idea, there are many different versions of the craft, such as the Resurs, Foton, and Bion. I think this could be a good idea to atleast think of, as it's a very important, and sadly somewhat forgotten part of space history. This is all just a suggestion though, even if you just think of it I think that'd be a success for me! Oh and, Hope everyone on this forum, and well, all of the KSP forums, is well
